/>\n強烈建議各區組織民衛隊，取代黑警職責<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">港鐵戰線:</span><br />\n全面係所有車站招貼: 元朗站逼市民落車被打，妄顧安危<br />\n一定要令每個站每個角落都見到<br />\n全面不合作運動，再加宣傳市民全面罷坐港鐵<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">其他紀律部隊戰線:</span><br />\n拉攏非警察的紀律部隊，要求表態，為違反紀律部隊職責的警察投訴"},{"pid":"fcff86b09642d72f7cd61f7fde7f76cd349303d4","tid":1347774,"uid":35830,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:46:31.000Z","msg":"點解你仲會用wechat<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09688ff1617ec0c97f06d8cc87b3c7a8d6d7556e","tid":1347774,"uid":281419,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:46:44.000Z","msg":"咪撚用wechat"},{"pid":"6fbbd695513be79f0fefadca47f5c688c3c8a5b4","tid":1347774,"uid":62749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:46:51.000Z","msg":"最多最多<br />\nsend Twitter, Facebook link<br />\n唔好發表任何意見"},{"pid":"ee14444f56e91df40806c3e04626b37705d8113d","tid":1347774,"uid":89514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:46:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"65f04994250083eb2fcf9da985b315b095ecd0d2","tid":1347774,"uid":279293,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fcff86b09642d72f7cd61f7fde7f76cd349303d4","tid":1347774,"uid":35830,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:46:31.000Z","msg":"點解你仲會用wechat<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:47:12.000Z","msg":"平時send嘢俾老母 sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d9b5c2f4d57e5aacfb0a202d211f0f951d13039","tid":1347774,"uid":61249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:47:33.000Z","msg":"剷左wechat佢啦"},{"pid":"4b64d686edd9fafeafda87487e1421afb40f4432","tid":1347774,"uid":119596,"like":0,"d